                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270111-6-off33 t18270111-6-crimeloc35"></join>, 2 watches, value 7l.; 1 seal, value 15s.; 1 watch-key, value 3d., and 4 sovereigns, the property of 
                     
